Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.00,0:02:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第八十五话\N迷走之旅 御神渡的陷阱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.23,0:02:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真田忍者群的碉堡在哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.70,0:02:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正确位置我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.71,0:02:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过肯定是在\N很前面的地方吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.54,0:02:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心 他们对于神圣的灵药\N应该知道什么吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.18,0:02:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很在意黑骑士团的动静
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.79,0:02:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们得到地图以后\N不可能不展开行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.73,0:02:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近真田忍者群的行动很怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.93,0:02:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许是因为知道了\N想得到灵药的黑骑士团的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.87,0:03:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了 弥彦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.21,0:03:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没体力啦？真没用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.78,0:03:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是 是肚子好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.08,0:03:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弥彦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.28,0:03:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 弥彦 弥彦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.02,0:03:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发高烧了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.09,0:03:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,振作点 弥彦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.99,0:03:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人在那
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.86,0:03:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是真田的人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.26,0:03:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们是什么人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.63,0:03:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.63,0:03:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来是猎人叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.17,0:03:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们不是可疑的坏人\N是因为这孩子突然病了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.17,0:03:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,振作点 弥彦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.18,0:03:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.02,0:03:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弥彦 你快喝下这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.65,0:03:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概是喝生水拉肚子\N我再三告诉他要注意的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.52,0:04:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弥彦一直喝泉水\N说那冰冰的好喝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.46,0:04:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心 喝下那个药汤\N马上就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.10,0:04:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 猎人先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.90,0:04:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 我才该惊吓到你们而道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.27,0:04:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有时来路不明的挖金矿的人\N会把这座山搞得乱七八糟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.48,0:04:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大叔在这座山上生活很久了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.38,0:04:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在这座山上出生长大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.02,0:04:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从祖先开始\N每一代都在这里当猎人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.85,0:04:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,倒是 你们来深山做什么呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.02,0:04:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们是来寻找神圣的灵药的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.86,0:04:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们按照这些文句
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.53,0:04:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先去调查了诹访大社
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.50,0:04:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是还是找不出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.43,0:04:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有没有听说过呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.64,0:04:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这我没听过呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.81,0:04:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.14,0:04:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.78,0:04:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诹访大社不光是信州地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.21,0:04:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它还是日本出名的圣地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.32,0:05:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在诹访地方\N有个只有住在山上的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.36,0:05:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,代代相传畏惧敬仰的神圣场所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.73,0:05:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.76,0:05:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在龙神湖畔的一个神社
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.70,0:05:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请问这个龙神湖是在哪里呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.23,0:05:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比这里还要深山的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.90,0:05:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,值得去查一查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.11,0:05:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.17,0:05:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是为你们好 还是算了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.24,0:05:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是山上居民都害怕\N会遭到作祟而不敢靠近的禁地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.08,0:05:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌 作祟这回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.52,0:05:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定是迷信了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.29,0:05:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.02,0:05:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,证据是常常在深夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.36,0:05:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从龙神湖的方向\N会传来可怕的龙叫声
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.93,0:05:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这可是我亲耳听见的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.40,0:05:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你的照顾 谢啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.87,0:05:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 弥彦哪有人\N道谢这么马虎的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.11,0:05:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.08,0:05:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是病人耶！\N你该温柔一点 丑八怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.08,0:05:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没用拳头揍你就不错了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.52,0:06:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.85,0:06:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弥彦看来是没问题了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.32,0:06:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们特地从东京过来\N我也不好拦阻你们了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.29,0:06:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是路上还是请多小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.36,0:06:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大叔你也保重啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.63,0:06:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么我们差不多该走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.13,0:06:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢您的照顾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.57,0:06:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人间处处有温暖这句话是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.44,0:06:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个大叔帮助我们很多呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.84,0:06:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是能在大叔说的龙神湖神社\N找到新线索就更好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.25,0:06:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.02,0:06:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么 绯村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.52,0:06:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 可能是我多心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.93,0:06:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你最好忘记今天的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.16,0:06:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以后你还想平安生活吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.43,0:06:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要他们踏入陷阱一步\N就再也无法脱身了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.81,0:07:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底要走去哪里呀别说是湖了\N连水洼都没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.25,0:07:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是呀 应该是这个方向的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.35,0:07:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再走不动的话就把你丢下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.06,0:07:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.83,0:07:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水蛭呀水蛭呀水蛭呀…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.33,0:07:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水蛭？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.60,0:07:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水蛭常在起雾时出现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.08,0:07:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里一定是龙神湖了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.72,0:07:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么在湖畔应该有神社了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.37,0:08:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此\N比想像的小确实是神社没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.11,0:08:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四龙向月亮升起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.14,0:08:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神渡时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.54,0:08:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通往虎口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.75,0:08:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四龙是指四根御柱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.85,0:08:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么向月亮升起是什么意思呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.32,0:08:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神渡的意思也不明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.03,0:08:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.83,0:08:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神渡时是指御神渡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.56,0:08:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,御神渡是指冬天寒冷的夜里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.27,0:08:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诹访湖面的结冰\N发出巨大声响裂开那件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.47,0:08:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是那是冬天耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.61,0:08:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是这点不解呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.64,0:08:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总之我们先确认御柱吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.51,0:08:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 大家分头寻找
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.42,0:08:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个石碑是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.09,0:08:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是道祖神吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.09,0:08:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里也有实在有点奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.63,0:09:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.56,0:09:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那边也有同样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.83,0:09:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在神社周围有四根
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.53,0:09:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么说这是御柱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.44,0:09:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是 四龙向月亮升起\N这要怎么升起呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.77,0:09:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道有什么机关吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.78,0:09:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,月亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.66,0:09:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以拿下来耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.83,0:09:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊什么什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.47,0:09:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 都是你乱来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.24,0:09:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对呀对呀 这一定是作祟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.11,0:09:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不对 是月球引力关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.04,0:09:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟大海有涨潮退潮一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.25,0:09:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是牛顿发现的\N万有引力的法则
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.98,0:09:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牛顿？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.39,0:09:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.49,0:10:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.66,0:10:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道是机关
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.24,0:10:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,升天之龙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.15,0:10:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四龙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.78,0:10:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.65,0:10:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.18,0:11:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水开始退了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.70,0:11:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会错了 这就是神渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.55,0:11:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由太郎！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.53,0:11:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不敢相信我的眼睛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.36,0:11:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,湖水竟然分成两半
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.16,0:11:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是呀 这是奇迹了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.50,0:11:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 这是人为的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.74,0:11:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人故意做的机关\N配合古文献的内容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.44,0:11:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.61,0:12:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.51,0:12:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么 这小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.73,0:12:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是秘密之门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.70,0:12:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是虎口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.71,0:12:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么 又要发生什么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.98,0:12:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 由太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.68,0:12:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心 进入这地方没问题吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.82,0:12:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.32,0:12:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办？是要进去还是撤回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.79,0:12:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.13,0:12:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由太郎！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.76,0:12:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿薰你们不必勉强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.00,0:13:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经跟博士约好了\N不能到这里又空手而回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.37,0:13:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.30,0:13:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别只有你自己摆酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.00,0:13:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姐 要怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.41,0:13:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还怎么办这么危险\N不能置之不管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.61,0:13:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是该这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.17,0:13:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是真正的\N不入虎穴焉得虎子呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.77,0:13:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到这里等于是成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.91,0:13:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们本来解不开谜题呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.08,0:13:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这下子开始走运了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.91,0:13:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但愿如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.31,0:13:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在道场都很神气的呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.72,0:13:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别发抖了 走快点啦 阿薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.32,0:13:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你别推我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.42,0:13:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.52,0:13:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很危险的弥彦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.70,0:14:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小薰\N弥彦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.73,0:14:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们在干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.67,0:14:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全关起来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.94,0:14:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛 屁股跌得好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.61,0:14:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家没有受伤吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.41,0:14:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小操 你好重耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.02,0:14:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绯村大色狼 笨蛋 可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.55,0:14:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个洞窟有点怪怪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.52,0:14:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像有大东西在移动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.16,0:14:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且向这边来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.99,0:14:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.30,0:14:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有东西向这里来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.87,0:14:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会被压扁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.60,0:14:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不快逃会被压扁的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.61,0:14:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么逃 这里三面都是墙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.74,0:14:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这情况交给我来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.32,0:14:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.45,0:15:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如此而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.25,0:15:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.46,0:15:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,后面后面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.26,0:15:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,后面怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.83,0:15:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左之助 剩下的交给我来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.66,0:15:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,土龙闪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.13,0:15:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.44,0:15:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是飞天御剑流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.94,0:15:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要塌陷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.01,0:15:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是土龙闪害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.48,0:15:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你应该下手轻一点的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.58,0:15:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.58,0:15:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路有两条 该往哪边走呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.99,0:15:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,包在我身上啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.76,0:15:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,依照我在赌场\N锻练出来的赌徒直觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.22,0:15:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这边！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.41,0:16:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是无底深渊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.88,0:16:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,掉下去就没救了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.65,0:16:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我们走这种路吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.92,0:16:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许另一条路比较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.89,0:16:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们太天真了不该相信\N左之助的赌徒直觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.99,0:16:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,经你一说我发现\N最近我在赌场常常赌输
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.96,0:16:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你现在才发现承认
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.36,0:16:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是这并不见得\N另一条路就是安全的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.47,0:16:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我们就往前走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.87,0:16:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.34,0:16:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.18,0:16:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很危险哦 由太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.02,0:16:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.02,0:16:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么 由太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.66,0:16:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了那一小块没用的石头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.86,0:16:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁说没用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.36,0:16:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是汉斯博士留下的重要东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.03,0:16:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋跟命比起来哪一个重要啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.03,0:16:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这两个东西是不能比较的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.97,0:16:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是担心你耶你讲这什么话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.84,0:16:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要你管啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.97,0:16:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以后再吵啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.37,0:17:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是呀现在第一要务是向前走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.44,0:17:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 快点吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.15,0:17:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.48,0:17:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.88,0:17:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.62,0:17:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这地方我不敢走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.99,0:17:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来 让我来背你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.04,0:17:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.20,0:17:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么 剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.77,0:17:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有点不好意思问
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.51,0:17:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,问就问呀 是什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.74,0:17:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是胖了一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.21,0:17:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才没有 没礼貌 你乱讲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.62,0:17:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是这样子吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.19,0:17:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你多心了 你太多心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.96,0:17:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿薰 你果然胖了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.23,0:18:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们真的能走到\N有神圣的灵药的地方吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.51,0:18:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,类似的情况\N不会一直持续下去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.84,0:18:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前方有东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.21,0:18:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由太郎！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.29,0:18:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到这里就没路了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.89,0:18:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下来我们该怎么办呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.33,0:18:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那段话的下半段
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.26,0:18:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迷失于无明黑暗中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.33,0:18:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,圣观音之手所指之处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.80,0:18:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将前往大富士的山麓之打开吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.14,0:18:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我记得是这么记载
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.30,0:18:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无明黑暗是指这个洞窟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.94,0:18:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是 观音的手是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.84,0:18:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么打开路呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.45,0:18:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.75,0:18:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完蛋了这下了真的束手无策了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.28,0:18:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.13,0:19:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有查出什么吗 由太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.73,0:19:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你拿这石头要做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.56,0:19:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想这石头一定有什么意义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.50,0:19:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该不会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.07,0:19:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小心点 由太郎\N搞不好是什么机关哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.52,0:19:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么 什么也没发生呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.92,0:19:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然 那只是没用的石头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.89,0:19:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.96,0:19:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们看这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.43,0:19:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.03,0:19:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.67,0:19:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.57,0:19:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能是水渗透进去的关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.34,0:19:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由太郎 看来方向放反了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.71,0:19:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手是刻向这一边的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.12,0:19:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.68,0:19:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来不像陷阱耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.72,0:20:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有点怪怪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.82,0:20:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了 阿薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.03,0:20:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,影子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.36,0:20:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,影子？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.37,0:20:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那地方有观音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.27,0:20:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,圣观音之手所指之处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.37,0:20:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是手！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.94,0:20:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.64,0:20:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由太郎！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.65,0:20:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,墙壁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.95,0:20:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.95,0:20:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神圣的灵药在这后面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.09,0:20:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成功了！由太郎！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.43,0:20:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迷失于无明黑暗中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.16,0:20:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,圣观音之手所指之处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.63,0:20:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将前往\N大富士的山麓之道打开吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.20,0:20:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,富士跟长生不老\N的发音相同(富士=不死）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.14,0:20:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是指示\N通往神圣灵药的地方呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.41,0:20:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 由太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.98,0:20:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好耶这下子宝物是我们的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.28,0:21:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来你们还不知道\N那些谜语的全部意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.35,0:21:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.53,0:21:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,黑骑士团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.63,0:21:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个女人是真田的头目\N她跟他们联手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.80,0:21:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽说一切都在我们计划中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.83,0:21:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是你们也挺有能耐\N打开最后一道门了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.74,0:21:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我该向你们道谢呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.74,0:21:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,计划？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.31,0:21:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那女人\N在讲什么莫名奇妙的话呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.41,0:21:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼 你讲话注意点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.91,0:21:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道是谁治好你的病的呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.02,0:21:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们好像中了敌人陷阱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.19,0:21:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个老人果然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.82,0:21:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老人你是说那猎人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.76,0:21:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,长年用枪的猎人身上\N应该有火药的味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.43,0:21:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我在那老人身上\N却什么也没感觉到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.37,0:21:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来那个老人是你伪装的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.14,0:22:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她说我们不知道\N全部的谜语是什么意思啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.84,0:22:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是说博士笔记上那最后一行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.94,0:22:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我告诉你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.68,0:22:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,圣观音的手所指之处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.68,0:22:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将前往\N大富士的山麓之道打开吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.59,0:22:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那条路非常险恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.59,0:22:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通往地狱深渊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.42,0:22:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地狱深渊 糟了
